instances.selector: background: transparent !important; /* Transparent background, not black */
instances.fullLine: background: transparent !important; /* Transparent background, not black */

instances.selector: z-index: 99999 !important; /* Higher than vortex to ensure it's on top */
instances.fullLine: z-index: 99999 !important; /* Higher than vortex to ensure it's on top */

instances.selector: z-index: 2147483647 !important; /* Maximum z-index for fullscreen compatibility */
instances.fullLine: z-index: 2147483647 !important; /* Maximum z-index for fullscreen compatibility */

instances.selector: overflow: visible !important; /* Changed from hidden to visible for tooltips */
instances.fullLine: overflow: visible !important; /* Changed from hidden to visible for tooltips */

instances.selector: overflow: visible !important; /* Ensure tooltips are visible */
instances.fullLine: overflow: visible !important; /* Ensure tooltips are visible */

instances.selector: position: relative !important; /* Required for absolute positioning of tooltip */
instances.fullLine: position: relative !important; /* Required for absolute positioning of tooltip */

instances.selector: ) !important; /* ABOVE dots: menu bottom (2rem) + dot height (12px) + gap (12px) */
instances.fullLine: ) !important; /* ABOVE dots: menu bottom (2rem) + dot height (12px) + gap (12px) */

instances.selector: transform: translateX(-50%) !important; /* Center the tooltip itself */
instances.fullLine: transform: translateX(-50%) !important; /* Center the tooltip itself */

instances.selector: transform: translateX(-50%) !important; /* Keep centered on hover */
instances.fullLine: transform: translateX(-50%) !important; /* Keep centered on hover */

instances.selector: bottom: calc(2rem + 12px + 6px) !important; /* Position above dots, just below tooltip */
instances.fullLine: bottom: calc(2rem + 12px + 6px) !important; /* Position above dots, just below tooltip */

instances.selector: border-top: 6px solid var(--accent-cyan) !important; /* Arrow pointing DOWN to dot */
instances.fullLine: border-top: 6px solid var(--accent-cyan) !important; /* Arrow pointing DOWN to dot */
